Description In this lecture, we introduce you to your very first RL algorithm, Epsilon Greedy. We start off by exploring a toy problem known as the &ldquo;multi armed bandit problem&rdquo; or in english- how to win at slot machines! We then dive down into how Epsilon-Greedy solves the bandit problem, go on a detour introducing OpenAi Gym (and why it is important!) and finally hand you over to your first exercise, solving the bandit problem in OpenAi Gym.
A written version of this lecture is also available on the StarAi blog.
